<br>
As far as we know, FoH is the ONLY guild to have completed the quests.  They figured out the quests completely on their own.  As far as I know, there was not even a hint of spoiler information available  2-3 months ago when they started.<br>
<br>
To date, no one we know has solved the Vex Thal key quest.  A LOT of people have been dilgently spending HOURS of in game time testing theories, getting faction, hailing NPCs, etc.  They then came to these boards and posted EVERYTHING they knew.  You then, using information you got from Safehouse, to further the quest, then come back here and &quot;tease&quot; everyone else.<br>
<br>
It is like the difference between Microsoft and Linux.  FoH is like Microsoft, in that they do not come to the safehouse for spoiler info and figure out everything out on their own. (Please no Microsoft cracks, I know this is a loose anology)  In essance, they own full rights to all their information.  We at the safehouse are more like Linux, in that we are a community of users working together to solve a problem.  And when we make a discovery based on information we got from the safehouse, it is our duty to report back.<br>
<br>
What you are doing is akin to getting the source code to Linux, making some changes, then claiming it to be your own product.<br>
<br>
